-Dont harcode

-You’re adding to the list inside @Composable:

 tasks.add(Task(1, "Task 1", "Description for Task 1", false))

 This runs every recomposition (whenever the UI updates).

 So each recomposition → adds Task 1 again → duplicates, and potential crashes.

 ⚡ Rule of Compose: Never modify state directly inside a composable body unless wrapped in a side-effect (LaunchedEffect, remember, etc.).

-